<p>For the email subject line use something specific like ‘Your GP appointment reminder’ or ‘NHS Vaccination Invitation’ rather than a generic ‘NHS invite’. Keeping subject lines short will make your email stand out in a patient’s inbox which means it is more likely to be opened and read.</p>

